---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="News Lancashire privacy policy. No tracking. No cookies. No personal data collected.">
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 1rem;">
    <h1 class="hero-headline">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Last updated: April 2026</p>
  </section>

  <div class="article-body">
    <h2>Summary</h2>
    <p>We do not collect personal data. We do not use cookies. We do not track you.</p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We use Cloudflare Web Analytics, a privacy-focused analytics service that collects
      aggregate page view data without using cookies, fingerprinting, or collecting personal
      information. No data is shared with third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>Newsletter</h2>
    <p>
      If you subscribe to our newsletter, we store your email address solely for the purpose of
      sending you news digests. You can unsubscribe at any time. We do not share your email
      with third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>Data sources</h2>
    <p>
      All data published on this site comes from publicly available official records
      (council transparency data, Companies House, Electoral Commission, Parliament,
      ONS Census, Home Office statistics). No private or personal data is scraped or published.
    </p>

    <h2>Hosting</h2>
    <p>This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare's privacy policy applies to infrastructure-level data processing.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy enquiries, contact Tom Pickup via the channels listed on our <a href="/about/">About page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
